ate galaxy shapes implies that\nthe galaxy population in the simulation is complete only to an r-band absolute\nmagnitude of <-20. Higher resolution simulations will be necessary to avoid\nextrapolation of the intrinsic alignment predictions to the range of\nluminosities probed by future surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2016 15:40:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Jun 2016 16:25:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-29"}
